-- SIV Portfolio receivers strike deal with Goldman
-- 
-- Tue Jun 17, 2008 10:54am EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2008/06/17/us-goldman-siv-confirmation-idUSWLA497820080617

 

 LONDON  (Reuters) - The receivers of SIV Portfolio Plc, formerly Cheyne Finance Plc, said in a statement on Tuesday they had agreed on the terms of a restructuring and a portfolio sale with Goldman Sachs Group ( GS.N ). 

 Reuters reported earlier on Tuesday that Goldman had nearly completed the long-awaited rescue of the $7 billion structured investment vehicle (SIV), formerly run by hedge fund Cheyne Capital. (Reporting by  Olesya Dmitracova )